title: Favor Has Been Released Into Your Future | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Favor Has Been Released Into Your Future | Joel Osteen
description:
When God created you, He lined up everything you need to reach your destiny. There is favor, opportunity and divine connections in your future! 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
